snippet.title: Super Mario Odyssey : Wuhu Kingdom Trailer NFGD 2021
snippet.description:
This trailer was featured in the Nintendo Fan Games Direct 2021! https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=PfKRN1Ejbho
I've worked hard on Wuhu Kingdom since 2019 and i still have a bunch of work to do for it to be finished! Be patient, as you will soon relax!
